11
00:04:06.453 --> 00:04:09.214
Blake. Blake.

12
00:04:09.352 --> 00:04:11.353
Blake.

13
00:04:11.492 --> 00:04:13.253
Did you hear what I just said?

14
00:04:13.391 --> 00:04:14.391
Yes. sir.

15
