18
00:04:19.637 --> 00:04:21.468
Uh...

19
00:04:21.606 --> 00:04:23.584
See. this is what I'm talking
about... you're not hearing me.

20
00:04:23.608 --> 00:04:26.611
You're off in your own
goddamn world somewhere.

21
