This place is beautiful.
It's also dangerous.

22
00:04:28.957 --> 00:04:32.479
You can survive if you
know exactly what to do.

23
00:04:32.617 --> 00:04:33.825
Yes. sir.

24
00:04:36.276 --> 00:04:39.900
People get taken from you...
... like that.

25
