It's not hard to die.

26
00:04:43.766 --> 00:04:45.940
It's the easiest
thing in the world.

27
00:04:46.078 --> 00:04:48.943
We are all...

28
00:04:49.081 --> 00:04:51.463
inches away from it.

29
00:04:51.601 --> 00:04:54.846
And I'm not always gonna be
around to watch over you.

30
00:04:54.984 --> 00:04:57.227
but I'm gonna make
damn sure that you know

31
00:04:57.366 --> 00:04:59.471
how to survive as...

32
00:05:32.470 --> 00:05:34.334
Blake.

33
00:05:38.924 --> 00:05:40.340
Blake.

34
00:07:03.802 --> 00:07:05.873
You know you need
to stay near me.

35
