391
00:31:18.911 --> 00:31:20.311
Okay. All right.
Charlotte. come on.

392
00:31:22.535 --> 00:31:23.640
Are you okay?

393
00:31:23.778 --> 00:31:24.824
- No. yeah. Yeah. Yeah.
- Yeah?

394
00:31:24.848 --> 00:31:26.091
Ginger. are you hurt at all?

395
00:31:26.229 --> 00:31:27.669
- No.
- Okay. come on.

396
00:31:27.747 --> 00:31:28.759
We got to go. We have
to find the house.

397
00:31:28.783 --> 00:31:30.063
Watch your step. Come on. honey.

398
00:31:30.198 --> 00:31:31.210
We got to move quick.

399
00:31:31.234 --> 00:31:33.581
Where it's safer. Come on.

400
00:31:33.719 --> 00:31:36.032
Careful. honey. Careful.
careful. careful.

401
00:31:37.171 --> 00:31:38.551
- Daddy. I'm tired.
- What?

402
00:31:38.689 --> 00:31:39.932
- I can't go.
- Okay.

403
00:31:41.900 --> 00:31:43.384
Charlotte.

404
00:31:43.522 --> 00:31:44.903
Okay. honey.

405
00:31:46.732 --> 00:31:48.354
Quick.

406
00:31:50.701 --> 00:31:52.048
Come on. I recognize this.

407
00:31:52.186 --> 00:31:53.566
We're close.

408
00:31:53.704 --> 00:31:55.165
I'm gonna put you down
here. honey. okay?

409
00:31:55.189 --> 00:31:57.122
- Okay.
- Give me your hand.

410
00:31:57.260 --> 00:31:58.364
Come on.

411
00:31:58.502 --> 00:31:59.617
- Come on.
- Careful.

412
00:31:59.641 --> 00:32:01.298
Be careful.

413
00:32:02.886 --> 00:32:04.750
Come on. Come on.

414
00:32:04.888 --> 00:32:06.648
This is it.

415
00:32:08.271 --> 00:32:09.997
Run.

416
00:32:10.135 --> 00:32:12.413
Run. honey.

417
00:32:12.551 --> 00:32:14.070
Go. honey.

418
00:32:15.243 --> 00:32:16.451
Come on.

419
00:32:16.589 --> 00:32:18.281
Come on. Come on.

420
00:32:18.419 --> 00:32:20.076
Come on.

421
00:32:25.805 --> 00:32:27.369
Daddy. hurry up.

422
00:32:27.393 --> 00:32:28.873
Daddy. hurry up!

423
00:32:28.912 --> 00:32:30.155
Come on. Get inside.

424
00:32:47.275 --> 00:32:48.967
Wait. Wait.

425
00:32:58.700 --> 00:33:00.161
- Stay right here.
- Daddy. where are you going?

426
00:33:00.185 --> 00:33:01.541
- I'll be right back.
- Daddy. Daddy.

427
00:33:01.565 --> 00:33:02.808
